	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Free day. I had some variety of grandiose plans for today. I was going to see so much of Paris that I&#8217;d be actually tired of it.<br />
That had been the plan. What I hadn&#8217;t planned on was how tired I was going to feel when I woke up.<br />
